==Gamilaraay==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ŋali/}}
===Etymology===
From Proto-Central New South Wales ''*ngali'', from Proto-Pama-Nyungan ''*ngali''.
===Pronoun===
'''ngali'''

# [[we|We]] two ''(first person dual pronoun)''
